cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use pccx, please cite it using the metadata in this file."
title: "pccx — open FPGA-oriented LLM inference accelerator"
abstract: >-
  pccx is the canonical architecture and specification repository for an
  FPGA-oriented LLM inference accelerator stack targeting Xilinx Kria
  KV260 (Zynq UltraScale+ ZU5EV).  It defines the ISA, memory hierarchy,
  documentation, roadmap, and release snapshots used by the
  implementation and tooling repositories in the pccx ecosystem.
type: software
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/pccxai/pccx"
url: "https://pccxai.github.io/pccx/"
authors:
  - family-names: Kim
    given-names: Hyunwoo
    # TODO(hkimw): set orcid once registered
